  text_playerStarter: {fileID: 1590294859}
  text_playerBench: {fileID: 1512085055}
  text_CurrentDefensiveStyle: {fileID: 2098788238}
  list_ReceiveThePos:
  - receives it! Let's go upfield!
  - took possession of the ball.
  - receives cleanly.
  - took the Zone Sphere and is powering forwards!
  - has secured the ball!
  - stole It with a beautiful right hook to the cheek. Ouch!
  - now OWNS the ball!
  - got the ball! But it ill be tough finding a gap in that defense!
  - has denied anyone else access to the Zone Sphere! Doesn't look like anyone can
    take it now!
  - captured the Zone Sphere! And what a dash that was!
  - shows 'em whoose Sphere that is!
  - is having no one else holding the Zone Sphere but him!
  - robbed the ball and won't look back.
  list_Shooting:
  - lines up for the shot!
  - blasts it across the arena!
  - takes the shot!
  - goes for it!
  - with an attempt to score!
  - rips one towards the target!
  - lets the Zone Sphere jet though the air!
  - fires the cannon!
  - Sparkles the arena with a shot!
  - shoots it right by the opponent's left year!
  - nearly hits the opponent with the shot!
  - lets it fly!
  - makes the shot loud and have everyone scared!
  - lets out the light show and lets the ball soar!
  - lets the ball scream!
  - blasts the Zone Sphere to rage on It's own!
  list_LosesBall:
  - gets scared and loses the ball.
  - gets robbed by the defender.
  - practically gave the ball for free.
  - lets it fall and the opponent grabs it.
  - tries to break through but gets pinned down.
  - got stolen!
  - has Lost the ball
  - got mugged of his Zone Sphere.
  - drops the ball. Opponent secures it!
  - got the Sphere nabbed from his hand
  - let's the ball be taken by hand.
  - offers the ball for mercy!
  - takes a left cross to the cheek and loses the ball!
  - takes it straight to the nose and away goes the Sphere!
  list_successShoot:
  - Nailed it! Bullseye !
  - Excellent execution guys! Keep up!
  - Exactly as we practiced. Very good.
  - BOOM! Exploded in the Score Zone!
  - Beautiful fireworks!
  - ZOOM! what a flight!
  - Uhh I like the light show!
  - Now THAT is what I'm talking about!
  - Oh yes! THAT was a shot!
  - 'Flew across the whole arena! Did you see that? '
  - UHH I LOVE the digital sound of the Sphere on the net!
  - Right on the fly!
  - Great Job Gunman!
  - THAT would make the cowboys proud!
  - The gun range will speak about it the whole year!
  list_FailShoot:
  - Almost! We have to keep trying.
  - "Off the mark. let\xB4s try again next."
  - Damn! Don't lose the rhythm!
  - Oh man... We'll be the joke of the gun range.
  - All according to plan...
  - Well that was anti-climatic.
  - Where did he even shoot at?
  - Wait did they really defend it?
  - How did they all even cordinate to defend it?
  - I mean... on the wall doesn't count!
  - Are you trying to kill the audience?
  - The Scoring Zone was RIGHT THERE!
  - I did not see that.... I did not see that.
  - no way this guy trained on the range...
  - Oh no... no no no....
  - This can't be.
  - what? just like that?
  list_successJuke:
  - Nice Juke! his ankles are broken now though.
  - Perfect ball control! Keep attacking like that!
  - Wow! You got him leaning!
  - What a dance!
  - Great Footwork!
  - Ha! They slipped! HAHAHAHA
  - Love when they get dizzy! Fantastic Juke!
  - Left them to eat digidust! great one!
  - And hose guys are still looking for you!
  - 'Those two got completelly bamboozled! '
  - '"Gotta Go Fast" the wise once said!'
  - Wait! Did he teleport or something?
  - Like a bullet! What are those legs?
  - My eyes didn't even follow thse moves!
  - Great slide under his shove!
  - Right past 'em!
  - Oh that poor fool! He didn't even see you go! ha haha!
  list_failJuke:
  - Turnover... Let's reset and make them pay next drive.
  - Damn! we fumbled this time.
  - We were careless, damn it.
  - Aand... he fell on the ground.
  - Did he seariouly fell face flat on the ground?
  - Even MY nose hurts from that punch.
  - He'll get up from that... any time now... any time...
  - That was some cartoon type of stuff..
  - Well if anything we're enterteining the crowd...
  - Nice footw... oh...
  - 'sad... '
  - Sad... just sad...
  - HAHAH... wait the fallen one is one of ours, I can't...
  - '* Muffled laughs * * " face flat on the ground..." * '
  - Oh hell nah!
  - No!... come back with our ball!
  - Tripped on his own foot...
  list_successPass:
  - Nice Pass!!!
  - Now that's what you call a perfect pass!
  - Stellar Pass!
  - Right into his hands!
  - Great choice of action!
  - The Sphere is in the right hands now!
  - He has been training that arm all right!
  - Man what a beautiful throw!
  - Passed right above his head!
  - All right! Now what do we do?
  - Great Positioning!
  - All right! That was a good move!
  - Good move!
  - Wise Choice!
  - A little tight, but responsible choice!
  list_failPass:
  - Oh no, his Gantlet malfunctioned!
  - Slipped through his fingers... so much for magnetism I guess
  - It must have been the wind! Right? Right?
  - He knows that was the opponent, right?
  - Well I gotta give props to those jumpy legs, opponent nabbed it.
  - ._.
  - What even was that?
  - ...
  - Yeah It was very crowded there...
  - He slapped his gauntlet away! Did you see that?
  - He could do it wheren't for that slap!
  - Well that punch would throw anyone's pass off.
  - Ok, we can fix it! We can fix it!
  - No big deal! We can retake It!
  list_Opp_FailedAttempt:
  - Good defense Guys!
  - Good work on defense!
  - Good job defending!
  - Great Move!
  - They almost got the chance! Great one guys!
  - Great Defense!
  - Ball is ours!
  - Zone Sphere Back into our hands!
  - Oof that was close!
  - Awesome! Now prepare for the counter-attack!
  - They'll regret losing the ball now!
  list_Opp_SucAttempt:
  - We let them score...
  - We need to put more pressure
  - More focus next Time!
  - All according to plan... right? right??
  - NO!
  - Just to let them have at least some points, right?
  - I'm passing out. I'm passing out...
  list_Personality:
  - Oh No! he is ignoring our instructions!
  - Wait! He is acting on his own!
  - No wait! He can't do that!
  - 'Dude! Such a hard head! Stop that! '
  - Go on! Move on your own! See if we care!
  - NO! Man... we gotta revise his paycheck!
  - Not another compulsionhead!
  - Oh there he goes alone again!
  - Someone catch that dude!
  - Hold Up! Wait! Does he has NO Discipline?
  - Oh not mutiny again!
  - He's deserting again!
  list_charge:
  - Charged up!
  - He's fired up!
  - Successful Charge!
  - Nice Sparkles! Static Chock!
  - Lit Up like a candle!
  - Onto them lighthouse!
  - Zap Zap!
  - Successfully Energised!
  - Shocking!
  list_chargeFail:
