  - Someone check if he's still breathing!
  - Oh no! Armor malfunction!
  - He fried up! Get the firefighters!
  - He shut down! Zap him back!
  list_shoveSucesses:
  - Pushed him back!
  - Created some space!
  - Successful Shove!
  - Goodbye defender!
  - Over-powered him!
  - Shoved him out of the way!
  - BOOM right in the face!
  - Ouch that probably hurts!
  - Nice Punch!
  - Hit him just like a train!
  - Nice Left!
  - Great Right!
  - Great one! But move fast, he'll be zapped back soon!
  - POW! Down he goes!
  - That's some shaolin stuff right there!
  - Ka-POW!
  - Straight to the chin!
  - Few decades ago this would leave a mark!
