      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6563504826612088725, guid: 30c6f40278f2a98469fe98cc26332de9, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Team Organization\nWhen you call a timeout (available at the start
        of the match or after each possession), the Team Organization screen appears.
        Here, you can:\n-Make substitutions to swap players and keep your team fresh.\n-Choose
        your defensive style to counter your opponent\u2019s attacks.\nYour defensive
        style affects gameplay: a more aggressive style may make it easier to stop
        the opponent\u2019s offense, but it will tire your players faster. Choose
        wisely, Boss!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
