    - target: {fileID: 6563504826612088725, guid: 30c6f40278f2a98469fe98cc26332de9, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Below, you''ll see the play options, which are available only when
        you have possession of the ball. Above each button, there''s an accuracy
        percentage showing your chance of success. You have three action choices:
        Pass, Shoot, or Use SP Skill. Let me explain the SP Skill now.'
